   "source": [
    "# ASF HyP3 SBAS InSAR Time-Series Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "**Complete workflow:** Data acquisition → MintPy SBAS inversion → Displacement maps, velocity maps, hotspot maps, coherence maps, and temporal displacement curves.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Outputs produced:**\n",
    "- Time-series displacement maps (LOS, mm)\n",
    "- Mean annual velocity / subsidence rate map (mm/yr)\n",
    "- Cumulative displacement map\n",
    "- Hotspot map (areas of significant deformation)\n",
    "- Coherence map\n",
    "- Temporal displacement curves for selected points\n",
    "\n",
    "**Data source options:** ASF HyP3 SDK (live pull) | Your existing ASF download script | Local storage\n",
    "\n",
    "**AOI masking:** Shapefile (.shp) or KMZ (.kmz) supported.\n",
    "\n",
    "> **References:** [MintPy](https://github.com/insarlab/MintPy) | [ASF HyP3 SDK](https://github.com/ASFHyP3/hyp3-sdk) | [ASF OpenSARlab Recipe Book](https://github.com/ASFOpenSARlab/opensarlab_MintPy_Recipe_Book)"
   ]
  },
